node.text: High School Graduation✔️ This year has been extremely difficult, especially with schooling. My panic attacks and seizure like shakes kept me in bed and unable to go to school for the entire first semester of school. Having to quit polo and seeing my friends every day was extremely difficult. But I joined an adult school and worked my ass off to finish. It was hard overcoming my mental and physical health issues. But I’m so happy and proud that I got through it triumphant. I couldn’t have done this without the love and support from my family and friends. I love you all 💕💕 #metoo

From the short time that I have known you, I have determined that you are one of the strongest people I know and you just simply radiate determination, kindness and love. You deserve the absolute best, I’m so incredibly happy for you 💛💛
congrats so much on graduating!!! so proud that you've made it through high school ♥️♥️♥️
I am a proud child!!! I love you so much and I am so excited to see where you go in life! Thank you for everything 💕💕💕
so proud of you sis you have come so far❤️

Congratulations Sarah 😍🎉
I will go to LA this year end! Say hello to Ruth💗
Aw congrats!!!🎉🎉 so proud go celebrate :)
